    "FVC, forced vital capacity; FEV1, forced expiratory volume in one second; PEF, peak expiratory flow; MMEF, maximal mid-expiratory flow; FEF75, forced expiratory flow at 75% of FVC; FEF50, forced expiratory flow at 50% of FVC; FEF25, forced expiratory flow at 25% of FVC.",
